<div class="questions">
  <div class="faq large-3 large-centered columns">
    <h4>Free?</h4>
    Yes, your photoshoot will be completely free. Well-photographed listings generate more interest and tours. We want the 42Floors community to succeed.
  </div>
  <div class="faq large-3 large-centered columns">
    <h4>When will my photos be live on 42Floors?</h4>
    Once your photographer uploads the photos from your shoot, our team reviews them. We want to make sure your photos are amazing, so this might take up to 2 weeks.
  </div>
  <div class="faq large-3 large-centered columns">
    <h4>How do I apply?</h4>
    Once you have confirmed your email address and verified your phone number, we'll be in contact and help you set up your listing.
  </div>
